Program: Outlook
Title: Ten years on: Inside the Moscow theatre siege
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00z7630
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 22 Oct 2012
Ten years after the Moscow theatre siege, we hear from survivor Svetlana Gubareva who was in the audience with her 13-year-old daughter Sacha and her American fiance Sandy Booker. Outlook's Jo Fidgen also talks to the award-winning wildlife photographer Paul Nicklen who risks life and limb to take photographs in some of the most inhospitable places on earth. Image: Bubble-jetting Emperors. Credit: Paul Nicklen Show less